WEBVTT

00:01:38.500 --> 00:01:44.300
"Unfold"

00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:47.500
(Episode 1)

00:03:00.208 --> 00:03:00.875
Please take a look.

00:03:00.876 --> 00:03:02.596
Do you still need to confirm it personally?

00:03:02.833 --> 00:03:03.833
No, thanks.

00:03:13.857 --> 00:03:15.357
(Scene cleaning fee)

00:03:15.381 --> 00:03:16.854
(Blood test report)

00:03:36.375 --> 00:03:37.750
Hello, Mr. Zhou.

00:03:38.375 --> 00:03:39.166
The boss has reserved a seat for you.

00:03:39.166 --> 00:03:39.708
This way, please.

00:03:40.125 --> 00:03:41.125
Good.

00:03:43.541 --> 00:03:44.541
Lao Bai is truly amazing.

00:03:44.791 --> 00:03:46.499
He said that he had
collected a wall full of wine.

00:03:46.500 --> 00:03:47.500
I still don't believe it.

00:03:47.833 --> 00:03:49.791
Yeah, he loves collecting things.

00:03:50.625 --> 00:03:52.225
Is there any whiskey with a peat flavor?

00:03:56.416 --> 00:03:58.291
These two bottles, and that bottle.

00:03:58.458 --> 00:04:00.541
It all smells like peat.

00:04:03.500 --> 00:04:05.220
Then, I'll have the same as that gentleman.

00:04:07.916 --> 00:04:09.125
Younger Master. Pour a glass.

00:04:38.041 --> 00:04:39.375
That is my boss's son.

00:05:22.984 --> 00:05:24.891
[Signage indicated a second-hand bookstore]

00:05:37.411 --> 00:05:40.491
[A message with instructions on
how to clean a scene, plus an address]

00:05:46.541 --> 00:05:48.125
A'Che, your dad's calling.

00:05:51.666 --> 00:05:52.666
Dad.

00:05:53.625 --> 00:05:55.625
Sorry, I was just tidying up books.

00:05:56.083 --> 00:05:57.083
What's wrong?

00:05:57.166 --> 00:05:58.000
Take a look at WeChat.

00:05:58.125 --> 00:05:59.125
Remember not to be late.

00:06:00.250 --> 00:06:00.791
Understood.

00:06:00.875 --> 00:06:01.833
Also, call A'Yun.

00:06:01.834 --> 00:06:03.082
She will need to work overtime
until nine o'clock tonight.

00:06:03.083 --> 00:06:04.124
A batch of used books will be arriving.

00:06:04.125 --> 00:06:05.666
Let her put it in the warehouse.

00:06:10.333 --> 00:06:12.434
Dad said a batch of books
will arrive at nine o'clock.

00:06:12.458 --> 00:06:13.458
Sister Xiao Yun.

00:06:13.666 --> 00:06:15.208
I have something to do tomorrow.

00:06:15.391 --> 00:06:16.225
Thanks for your hard work.

00:06:16.250 --> 00:06:17.250
It's nothing.

00:06:17.291 --> 00:06:18.083
Just go ahead and do your own thing.

00:06:18.083 --> 00:06:20.822
The boss certainly can't pay me as
the store manager for doing nothing.

00:06:20.958 --> 00:06:22.518
Give me these books. I'll take them in.

00:06:23.791 --> 00:06:24.791
Here you are.

00:07:39.208 --> 00:07:40.208
Dad.

00:07:42.333 --> 00:07:43.333
Dad.

00:08:14.375 --> 00:08:16.250
Who is the deceased to you?

00:08:17.500 --> 00:08:18.750
He is my adoptive father.

00:08:19.833 --> 00:08:22.208
The preliminary diagnosis is sudden death.

00:08:22.875 --> 00:08:25.625
Perhaps the old gentleman was too exhausted
from his daily work.

00:08:27.041 --> 00:08:29.000
Could there be other possibilities?

00:08:31.500 --> 00:08:33.125
That depends on the autopsy results.

00:08:33.458 --> 00:08:35.101
Please go outside to sign the consent form.

00:08:35.125 --> 00:08:36.375
Just go back and wait for the news.

00:08:40.208 --> 00:08:43.230
Clearly, in the past three years,
none of you have come to see me work.

00:08:44.583 --> 00:08:46.041
Why are you here?

00:09:01.958 --> 00:09:02.958
Excuse me.

00:09:03.541 --> 00:09:04.541
Zhou Chen.

00:09:04.708 --> 00:09:05.708
Nice to see you again.

00:09:05.875 --> 00:09:07.235
I saw you in the bar before.

00:09:12.875 --> 00:09:14.125
Are you Lao Bai's son?

00:09:15.041 --> 00:09:16.851
I have some work that I
need to coordinate with him.

00:09:16.875 --> 00:09:18.541
But we can't get in touch with him now.

00:09:26.291 --> 00:09:27.291
What's wrong?

00:09:28.875 --> 00:09:30.041
My dad

00:09:32.083 --> 00:09:33.291
has passed away.

00:09:39.041 --> 00:09:40.041
I'm so sorry.

00:09:42.791 --> 00:09:43.791
It's nothing.

00:09:47.541 --> 00:09:49.059
So what's the reason for Lao Bai's death?

00:09:49.083 --> 00:09:50.332
Wasn't he in good health?

00:09:50.333 --> 00:09:51.613
How could it happen so suddenly?

00:09:53.743 --> 00:09:54.743
It's not clear yet.

00:09:59.500 --> 00:10:00.500
This is my business card.

00:10:01.041 --> 00:10:02.583
If you need any help in the future,

00:10:02.708 --> 00:10:03.988
feel free to contact me anytime.

00:10:06.291 --> 00:10:07.416
So,

00:10:07.625 --> 00:10:09.785
what is the matter
you need to coordinate with my dad?

00:10:10.916 --> 00:10:13.856
I am staff member of the medical
institution, responsible for organ donation.

00:10:14.750 --> 00:10:17.148
I coordinated with your
father over organ sourcing.

00:10:19.333 --> 00:10:22.291
I don't really understand how my father was
connected to anything related to organ donation.

00:10:23.875 --> 00:10:24.875
If there is any news,

00:10:24.958 --> 00:10:26.198
I will contact you immediately.

00:10:28.250 --> 00:10:28.666
It's nothing.

00:10:29.125 --> 00:10:29.666
No hurry.

00:10:30.041 --> 00:10:31.681
Take care of your father's affairs first,

00:10:34.625 --> 00:10:35.625
I'll head out first.

00:10:35.875 --> 00:10:36.875
Take care on the road.

00:11:22.138 --> 00:11:23.538
[SMS: January 22, Minhua
Private, Liver, 220000]

00:11:44.438 --> 00:11:45.063
Hello?

00:11:45.236 --> 00:11:46.236
It's me.

00:11:46.260 --> 00:11:47.260
Bai Che.

00:11:48.708 --> 00:11:49.708
It's you.

00:11:50.000 --> 00:11:51.000
What's wrong?

00:11:51.791 --> 00:11:53.416
I sorted through my father's belongings,

00:11:53.791 --> 00:11:56.017
unfortunately, I couldn't
find any relevant information.

00:11:56.041 --> 00:11:57.000
It's okay.

00:11:57.001 --> 00:11:58.416
Thank you very much anyway.

00:11:59.208 --> 00:12:00.166
The Minhua Hospital

00:12:00.167 --> 00:12:02.007
also took the initiative
to contact us, today.

00:12:02.208 --> 00:12:03.375
Minhua?

00:12:03.708 --> 00:12:04.708
What's wrong?

00:12:06.791 --> 00:12:07.791
It's nothing.

00:12:08.375 --> 00:12:09.375
Alright.

00:12:09.541 --> 00:12:10.642
Let's just leave it for now.

00:12:10.666 --> 00:12:11.666
Bye-bye.

00:12:12.208 --> 00:12:13.208
Bye-bye.

00:12:43.000 --> 00:12:50.000
(From Dad: January 28, Mingyue Pavilion,
Hexi District, No. 366, Building 3, Room 702)